Lagos – A young man who is into Information Technology has open up on how he has been assessing the panties of ladies in Lagos with ease. Relationship adviser and blogger, Joro Olumofin has shared the story of a guy who has been sleeping with several ladies, totalling 16 this year. According to him, he didn’t enjoy such a ‘privilege’ when he was broke last year. He presently feels bad about the kind of lifestyle he is living and hopes for a change. This gist has caused an outrage among ladies online. Read his story below: Source